{
  "stem": "26465.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So he took me to the washroom, and I washed my blood off.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And he took me to the square.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "There were people already sorted out-- women separated from men.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And there were no children anymore.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "He took me to their women's place.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And there were a lot of women.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Some really sobbing, crying, and-- I didn't know what was happening, but I knew that it was something terrible happening.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And the neighbor next to me told me, they took her children.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "They took her children.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I ask her, where did they take-- where did they take them?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she said, probably to burn.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They will burn them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I got scared, thinking this woman lost her mind!",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we are going to lose our minds, here.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't believe that one could burn a child alive-- or whatever that was.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we stood there for the roll call, and they gave us papers-- slip of paper.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they asked us to line up, two by two.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they drove us-- or rather-- I don't call it 'driving,' when you are being escorted-- you're on foot-- to someplace where we had to strip.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And men were around-- Gestapo-- looking at us, staring at us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We were very, very terribly not only ashamed but I'd call it violated, in that way.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then we had to give our clothes to-- apparently to delouse it-- to delouse our clothes.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And so they put numbers on this-- on the clothes-- and asked us to remember the numbers.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we went into this big place, and we had to wash our heads in some kind of a very burning stuff.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There were troughs alongside a wall, and you stood in there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You line up-- everybody was lining up around the troughs.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
